  "title": "🌟 Brand Glow-Up Executive [No Experience Needed] - Travelling Opportunities🌟",
  "description": "<p>📣 <strong>Brand Glow-Up Executive</strong> 🚀</p><p>Looking for a job that’s active, social, and actually helps you grow? Welcome to <strong>Valor Organisation</strong> — a high-energy marketing team in Singapore where you get real exposure, real training, and real results 💥</p><p>🎯 <strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong><br />🔥 Represent brands through fun marketing outreach campaigns<br />💬 Talk to people, share brand messages, and build connections<br />🤝 Work closely with a supportive, driven team<br />📈 Learn sales, communication, and marketing skills on the job</p><p>💎 <strong>What You’ll Get</strong><br />✨ Full training provided — no experience needed<br />🎉 Fun, positive team culture that celebrates wins<br />✈️ Opportunities to travel and gain new experiences<br />💼 Skills that build confidence and future career growth</p><p>💪 <strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong><br />✅ Fresh grads / ORD completed / Career switchers<br />✅ Energetic, outgoing, and open to learning<br />✅ Team players who enjoy engaging with people</p><p>🚀 <strong>No boring desk job here. If you’re ready to step out, learn fast, and grow — apply now!</strong></p>",
